cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.LG

The paper deals with access control policies and cryptography protocols for secure access to vehicular on-board units from smartphones. This involves security and privacy concerns related to both computer systems (cs.CR) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the development of a protocol suite (cs.SE) and the use of cryptography (cs.CY) to ensure appropriate security. Finally, the implementation of the proposed approach involves the use of modern smartphones (cs.LG).
